<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{ page_title }} — {{ shop.name }}</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Syne:wght@400;600;700;800&family=DM+Sans:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,500;1,300&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  {{ content_for_header }}
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0a0a0f;
      --surface: #111118;
      --surface2: #1a1a24;
      --accent: #00e5ff;
      --accent2: #7c3aed;
      --accent3: #f59e0b;
      --text: #f0f0f5;
      --muted: #8888aa;
      --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
      --glow: 0 0 40px rgba(0,229,255,0.15);
    }
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 300;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }
    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 256 256' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='noise'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23noise)' opacity='0.03'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 0;
      opacity: 0.4;
    }
    /* NAV */
    .site-nav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      padding: 20px 48px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      background: rgba(10,10,15,0.85);
      backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .site-logo {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--text);
    }
    .site-logo span { color: var(--accent); }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 36px; list-style: none; align-items: center; }
    .nav-links a {
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text); }
    .nav-cart {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #000 !important;
      padding: 10px 22px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-weight: 500 !important;
      font-size: 0.85rem !important;
      letter-spacing: 0.02em !important;
      text-transform: none !important;
      transition: all 0.2s !important;
    }
    .nav-cart:hover { background: #fff !important; }
    /* MAIN */
    main { padding-top: 80px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    /* MARQUEE */
    .marquee-wrap {
      overflow: hidden;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 16px 0;
      background: var(--surface);
    }
    .marquee-track {
      display: flex;
      gap: 48px;
      animation: marquee 20s linear infinite;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .marquee-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .marquee-item span { color: var(--accent); }
    @keyframes marquee {
      from { transform: translateX(0); }
      to { transform: translateX(-50%); }
    }
    /* BUTTONS */
    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #000;
      padding: 16px 36px;
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 500;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.25s;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: #fff;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 40px rgba(0,229,255,0.25);
    }
    .btn-secondary {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 6px;
      transition: color 0.2s;
      background: none;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover { color: var(--text); }
    /* SECTION LABELS */
    .section-label {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
    }
    .section-label::before { content: ''; width: 24px; height: 1px; background: var(--accent); }
    .section-title {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      line-height: 1.1;
    }
    /* FEATURES */
    .features-section {
      padding: 80px 48px;
      background: var(--surface);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .features-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 32px;
      margin-top: 64px;
    }
    .feature { text-align: center; }
    .feature-icon {
      width: 56px; height: 56px;
      background: rgba(0,229,255,0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0,229,255,0.15);
      border-radius: 16px;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
    }
    .feature h3 { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .feature p { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; }
    /* FOOTER */
    .site-footer {
      background: var(--surface);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 60px 48px 32px;
    }
    .footer-top {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 48px;
      margin-bottom: 48px;
    }
    .footer-brand p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.88rem; line-height: 1.7; margin-top: 16px; max-width: 280px; }
    .footer-col h4 {
      font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .footer-col ul { list-style: none; }
    .footer-col ul li { margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .footer-col ul li a { color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.88rem; transition: color 0.2s; }
    .footer-col ul li a:hover { color: var(--text); }
    .footer-bottom {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding-top: 24px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--muted);
    }
    /* PRODUCT CARDS */
    .products-section { padding: 100px 48px; }
    .products-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: flex-end;
      margin-bottom: 64px;
    }
    .products-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
    }
    .product-card {
      background: var(--surface);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--text);
      display: block;
    }
    .product-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-6px);
      border-color: rgba(0,229,255,0.2);
      box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.4), var(--glow);
    }
    .product-card-img {
      height: 320px;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
      background: var(--surface2);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .product-card-img img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; transition: transform 0.4s; }
    .product-card:hover .product-card-img img { transform: scale(1.05); }
    .product-card-img::after {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent 50%, var(--surface));
    }
    .product-card-info { padding: 20px 24px 24px; }
    .product-card-type { font-size: 0.72rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .product-card-title { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.3; }
    .product-card-footer { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; }
    .product-card-price { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 1.4rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent); }
    .product-card-price s { font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 400; margin-right: 8px; }
    .product-card-btn {
      width: 42px; height: 42px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #000;
      font-size: 1.3rem;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: all 0.2s;
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .product-card-btn:hover { background: #fff; transform: scale(1.1); }
    /* PRODUCT PAGE */
    .product-page { padding: 48px; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 64px; max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .product-gallery img { width: 100%; border-radius: 20px; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .product-info-block { padding-top: 24px; }
    .product-info-block h1 { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 16px; line-height: 1.2; }
    .product-price-block { margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .product-price-main { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--accent); }
    .product-price-compare { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--muted); text-decoration: line-through; margin-left: 12px; }
    .product-desc { color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.8; margin-bottom: 32px; font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .product-variants { margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .product-variants label { font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); display: block; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .variant-btn {
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--text);
      border-radius: 100px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      margin-right: 8px;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .variant-btn.active, .variant-btn:hover { background: var(--accent); color: #000; border-color: var(--accent); }
    .add-to-cart-btn {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 18px;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #000;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 100px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      transition: all 0.25s;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .add-to-cart-btn:hover { background: #fff; transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(0,229,255,0.25); }
    .product-badges { display: flex; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .product-badge-item { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--muted); }
    /* CART PAGE */
    .cart-page { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 48px; }
    .cart-page h1 { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 48px; }
    .cart-line { display: flex; gap: 24px; align-items: center; padding: 24px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .cart-line img { width: 80px; height: 80px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 12px; background: var(--surface2); }
    .cart-line-info { flex: 1; }
    .cart-line-title { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .cart-line-price { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }
    .cart-totals { padding: 32px 0; }
    .cart-total-row { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--muted); }
    .cart-total-row.final { font-family: 'Syne', sans-serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--text); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 16px; margin-top: 8px; }
    .cart-total-row.final span:last-child { color: var(--accent); }
    /* ANIMATIONS */
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(24px); }
      to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    .fade-up { animation: fadeUp 0.8s ease both; }
    /* RESPONSIVE */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .site-nav { padding: 16px 24px; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .products-section, .features-section { padding: 60px 24px; }
      .products-header { flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; align-items: flex-start; }
      .features-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .footer-top { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 32px; }
      .product-page { grid-template-columns: 1fr; padding: 24px; gap: 32px; }
      .cart-page { padding: 24px; }
      .site-footer { padding: 40px 24px 24px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav class="site-nav">
  <a href="/" class="site-logo">Home<span>Smart</span> Italia</a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="/collections/all">Prodotti</a></li>
    <li><a href="/collections/smart-home">Smart Home</a></li>
    <li><a href="/collections/cucina">Cucina</a></li>
    <li><a href="/pages/contatti">Contatti</a></li>
    <li>
      <a href="/cart" class="nav-cart">
        🛒 Carrello
        {% if cart.item_count > 0 %}
          ({{ cart.item_count }})
        {% endif %}
      </a>
    </li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
<main>
  {{ content_for_layout }}
</main>

<!-- MARQUEE -->
<div class="marquee-wrap">
  <div class="marquee-track">
    <div class="marquee-item"><span>⚡</span> Smart Home</div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span>🍳</span> Gadget Cucina</div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span>📦</span> Spedizione Veloce</div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span>🔒</span> Pagamenti Sicuri</div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span>↩️</span> Reso Gratuito 30gg</div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span>🌟</span> Qualità Garantita</div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span>📱</span> Controllo da App</div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span>💡</span> Risparmio Energetico</div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span>⚡</span> Smart Home</div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span>🍳</span> Gadget Cucina</div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span>📦</span> Spedizione Veloce</div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span>🔒</span> Pagamenti Sicuri</div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span>↩️</span> Reso Gratuito 30gg</div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span>🌟</span> Qualità Garantita</div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span>📱</span> Controllo da App</div>
    <div class="marquee-item"><span>💡</span> Risparmio Energetico</div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- FEATURES -->
<section class="features-section">
  <div style="text-align:center;">
    <div class="section-label" style="justify-content:center;">Perché sceglierci</div>
    <h2 class="section-title">Qualità e servizio prima di tutto</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="features-grid">
    <div class="feature">
      <div class="feature-icon">🚚</div>
      <h3>Spedizione Rapida</h3>
      <p>Consegna in 7-15 giorni lavorativi in tutta Italia con tracciamento in tempo reale.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <div class="feature-icon">🔒</div>
      <h3>Pagamenti Sicuri</h3>
      <p>Carte di credito, Apple Pay e Google Pay. Transazioni protette con crittografia SSL.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <div class="feature-icon">↩️</div>
      <h3>Reso Gratuito 30gg</h3>
      <p>Non sei soddisfatto? Rimborso completo entro 30 giorni, senza domande.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature">
      <div class="feature-icon">💬</div>
      <h3>Supporto Italiano</h3>
      <p>Assistenza clienti in italiano 7 giorni su 7. Rispondiamo entro 24 ore.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->
<footer class="site-footer">
  <div class="footer-top">
    <div class="footer-brand">
      <a href="/" class="site-logo">Home<span>Smart</span> Italia</a>
      <p>Rendiamo la tua casa più intelligente, un prodotto alla volta. Selezioniamo solo gadget di qualità per la tua smart home e la tua cucina.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-col">
      <h4>Prodotti</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/collections/smart-home">Smart Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="/collections/cucina">Casa & Cucina</a></li>
        <li><a href="/collections/all">Tutti i prodotti</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-col">
      <h4>Supporto</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/pages/spedizioni">Spedizioni</a></li>
        <li><a href="/pages/resi">Resi e rimborsi</a></li>
        <li><a href="/pages/contatti">Contattaci</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-col">
      <h4>Legale</h4>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/policies/privacy-policy">Privacy Policy</a></li>
        <li><a href="/policies/terms-of-service">Termini d'uso</a></li>
        <li><a href="/policies/refund-policy">Politica Resi</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="footer-bottom">
    <span>© {{ 'now' | date: "%Y" }} HomeSmart Italia. Tutti i diritti riservati.</span>
    <span>Made with ❤️ in Italia</span>
  </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
